{"tid":1478632,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個轉貼上內地網 話比大陸仔知MUD撚野係中共","createTime":"2019-08-16T15:02:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T15:03:57.000Z","uid":268321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7397ee7e2bf6874b4a19b1b12259297887bb40d0","tid":1478632,"uid":268321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:02:46.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一人一個轉貼上內地網絡話比大陸仔知MUD撚野係中共</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://據澳洲news.com.au\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E6%93%9A%E6%BE%B3%E6%B4%B2news.com.au&d=GZKRZRfhFQ75XgsIw24e0ad04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=fa153a38\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">據澳洲news.com.au</a>報導，一名被關押一年多的婦女告訴法國24電視台，她在新疆西部地區的一所監獄裡反復被醫生注射了一種物質。<br />\n<br />\n「我們不得不通過（牢房）門上的一個小開口伸出手臂(注射)，」54歲的前被拘留者加利洛娃（Gulbahar Jalilova）說，「我們很快就意識到，被注射藥物後，我們再也沒有來例假。」<br />\n<br />\n她和其他50多名女性被塞進一個小小的牢房裡。加利洛娃說，「我們就像是一塊肉一樣（被任意宰割）。」<br />\n<br />\n最近，另一名30歲的女性圖爾松（Mehrigul Tursun）在大赦國際的會議上講述了一個類似的故事：她在不知不覺中已經被強行絕育了。她說，在2017年被監禁期間，她被迫服用一種藥，之後「一個星期內感到疲累，失去了記憶並感到憂鬱沮喪」。幾個月後她被釋放，並被診斷患有精神病，現在她住在美國。那裡的醫生後來告訴她，她已經被絕育了。<br />\n<br />\n這兩名婦女都是維吾爾族穆斯林女性，曾被中共當局關押，強迫進行「再教育」。估計目前有100萬維吾爾人被關押。過去曾被關押在「再教育營」而現居住在西方國家的維吾爾族婦女說，她們被迫流產，包括懷孕後期也被強制墮胎。<br />\n<br />\n中文Source: <a href=\"http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/19/8/15/n11456069.htm?fbclid=IwAR3SQH6HKjvVzKUUCdBLto3mEdex4Ma9gziHZdczQd6Hn4h8_RqoUmbf3-A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fb5%2F19%2F8%2F15%2Fn11456069.htm%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3SQH6HKjvVzKUUCdBLto3mEdex4Ma9gziHZdczQd6Hn4h8_RqoUmbf3-A&d=GZKRZRfhFQ75XgsIw24e0ad04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=f7b50e2b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/19/8/15/n11456069.htm?fbclid=IwAR3SQH6HKjvVzKUUCdBLto3mEdex4Ma9gziHZdczQd6Hn4h8_RqoUmbf3-A</a><br />\n<br />\n英文Source: <a href=\"https://www.news.com.au/world/asia/chinas-sickening-acts-on-female-prisoners-at-reeducation-camps/news-story/34d531c19a5bb060881a76ac8b478609\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news.com.au%2Fworld%2Fasia%2Fchinas-sickening-acts-on-female-prisoners-at-reeducation-camps%2Fnews-story%2F34d531c19a5bb060881a76ac8b478609&d=GZKRZRfhFQ75XgsIw24e0ad04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=83a480dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.news.com.au/world/asia/chinas-sickening-acts-on-female-prisoners-at-reeducation-camps/news-story/34d531c19a5bb060881a76ac8b478609</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">大陸網<br />\n知乎: <a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zhihu.com%2F&d=GZKRZRfhFQ75XgsIw24e0ad04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=ff87fcb4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.zhihu.com/</a><br />\n百度貼吧: <a href=\"https://tieba.baidu.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftieba.baidu.com%2F&d=GZKRZRfhFQ75XgsIw24e0ad04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=3e792de1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tieba.baidu.com/</a><br />\n豆瓣: <a href=\"https://www.douban.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.douban.com%2F&d=GZKRZRfhFQ75XgsIw24e0ad04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=33f2d999\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.douban.com/</a><br />\n微博: <a href=\"https://www.weibo.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.weibo.com%2F&d=GZKRZRfhFQ75XgsIw24e0ad04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=5a86c8f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.weibo.com/</a></span>"},{"pid":"11e23e5f8c6db0d58e989ed9775f9d8d320f3fcf","tid":1478632,"uid":268321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:03:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b093563ae036c1c3cca51a15617e6c39bfd14e10","tid":1478632,"uid":268321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T15:03:23.000Z","